# Day 4 — Search & Text Processing

## 📌 Overview
On Day 4, I practiced searching, filtering, counting, sorting, and editing text using essential Linux commands. These skills are important for log analysis and cloud security tasks.

---

## 🛠 Commands Practiced

### 🔍 grep — Search Text
- Search for specific words inside files
```bash
grep "error" test.txt
grep -i "failed" /var/log/auth.log
